trans-unit.source: Enumerates the contents of the immutable hash set without allocating any memory.
trans-unit.target: 列舉不可變雜湊集的內容而不配置任何記憶體。

trans-unit.source: **NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">about immutable collections and how to install</see>)
trans-unit.target: **NuGet 套件**：<see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">關於固定集合及其安裝方法</see>)
此型別具備執行緒安全。

trans-unit.source: Gets the element at the current position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 取得位於目前列舉值位置的項目。

trans-unit.source: The element at the current position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 位於目前列舉程式位置的項目。

trans-unit.source: Releases the resources used by the current instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet`1.Enumerator" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 將 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet`1.Enumerator" /> 類別的目前執行個體所使用的資源釋出。

trans-unit.source: Advances the enumerator to the next element of the immutable hash set.
trans-unit.target: 將列舉程式前移至不可變雜湊集的下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the enumerator was successfully advanced to the next element; <see langword="false" /> if the enumerator has passed the end of the hash set.
trans-unit.target: 如果列舉程式成功前移至下一個項目，則為 <see langword="true" />；如果列舉程式超過雜湊集的結尾，則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The hash set was modified after the enumerator was created.
trans-unit.target: 建立列舉值之後，雜湊集已修改。

trans-unit.source: Sets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the hash set.
trans-unit.target: 將列舉程式設定至它的初始位置，就在雜湊集中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: The hash set was modified after the enumerator was created.
trans-unit.target: 建立列舉值之後，雜湊集已修改。
